{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Continuous Media","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Continuous_Media","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>CSS 可以用在許多不同的地方，印刷媒體便是一種。有些排版用的 CSS 會因為所處環境的不同而有不一樣的效果。</p>\n<p>連續性媒體 (continuous media) 指的就是這樣一種環境，其中的內容不是以片段呈現，而是持續更迭。比方說顯示在螢幕上的網頁內容、語音內容都是連續性媒體。</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"CSS 可以用在許多不同的地方，印刷媒體便是一種。有些排版用的 CSS 會因為所處環境的不同而有不一樣的效果。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Continuous Media","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Médias continus","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"連続的メディア (Continuous Media)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Continuous Media","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/glossary/continuous_media","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/glossary/continuous_media/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary","title":"術語表"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Continuous_Media","title":"Continuous Media"}],"pageTitle":"Continuous Media - 術語表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}